* Bugs:
  * Text dragging sometimes drags the whole schematic to a non-grid position making the schematic unusable
  	* Steps to reproduce: 1. Make a schematic, 2. Add text, 3. Select all (e.g. Ctrl+A), 4. Move all by dragging from a text element, 5. Chaos.

